#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu and Toolbar Items"
msgstr "Stavke menija i alatne trake"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&stage; presents different types of interfaces for you to interact with the "
"program. Perhaps the most familiar type of interface is the menu which "
"appears on the top of the &stage; window."
msgstr ""
"&stage; predstavlja različite tipove sučelja za vašu interakciju sa "
"programom. Možda najpoznatiji tip sučelja je meni koji se pojavljuje na vrhu "
"&stage; prozora."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the menu items gives you a list of commands from which you can "
"choose the one you want. Many of the commands can also be accessed directly "
"by holding down &Ctrl; or &Alt; and pressing another key on your keyboard. "
"In the next section, each of the menu commands is described in brief."
msgstr ""
"Klik na stavke izbornika vam daje popis naredbi iz kojih možete odabrati one "
"koje želite. Većini naredbi može se pristupiti izravno pritiskom na &Ctrl-; "
"ili &Alt; i pritiskom na drugu tipku na tastaturi. U sljedećem poglavlju, "
"svaki od naredbi izbornika je opisan ukratko."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Toolbars"
msgstr "Alatne trake"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manipulating the Toolbars"
msgstr "Manipulacija alatne trake"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the menus, &stage; also has a toolbar. The toolbar consists "
"of a collection of icons. A toolbar icon often presents a convenient "
"shortcut to a command that is found in one of the menus."
msgstr ""
"Osim izbornika, &stage; također ima alatnu traku. Alatna traka se sastoji od "
"kolekcije ikona. Ikona alatne trake često predstavlja zgodan prečac za "
"komandu koja se nalazi u jednom od menija."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move the unlocked toolbar around by dragging the handle at the left. "
"The unlocked toolbar can be <quote>docked</quote> or attached to any side of "
"the &stage; window. If you like, you can also have the toolbar <quote>float</"
"quote> in its own window, separated from the main &stage; window."
msgstr ""
"Možete premjestiti otključanu alatnu traku povlačenjem ručice na lijevoj "
"strani. Otključana alatna traka može biti <quote>dokovana</quote> ili "
"prikačena na bilo koju stranu &stage; prozora. Ako želite, možete imati "
"alatnu traku koja  <quote>lebdi</quote> u svom prozoru, odvojena od glavnog "
"&stage; prozora."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't like dragging toolbars around, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"click on the handle and a menu pops up."
msgstr ""
"Ako ne volite povlačiti alatne trake okolo,  <mousebutton>desni</"
"mousebutton> klik na ručicu i meni će se pojaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choosing the item <guisubmenu>Text Position</guisubmenu> leads to an "
"additional menu which lets you control the appearance of the items in "
"toolbar. This additional cascading menu is shown in the screenshot below:"
msgstr ""
"Odabir stavke <guisubmenu>Pozicija teksta</guisubmenu>vodi na dodatni meni "
"koji vam omogućuje kontrolu izgleda stavki na alatnoj traci. Ovaj dodatni "
"kaskadni meni je prikazan na screenshotu ispod:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Text Position</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pozicija teksta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Text Position</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pozicija teksta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to display the toolbar items as text instead of icons, or "
"even to combine both icons and text. If you want both text and icons, the "
"cascading menu allows you to select whether the text appears beside the "
"icons or below them."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati da prikažete stavke alatne trake kao tekst umjesto ikona, "
"ili čak kombinacija ikona i teksta. Ako želite oboje, ikone i teskt, "
"kaskadni meni dopušta da označite da li će se tekst pojaviti pored ikona ili "
"ispod njih."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In icons only view, if you don't know what a particular icon means, you can "
"hold the mouse over the icon, and after a second or so, a little hint pops "
"up in a highlighted text box."
msgstr ""
"U pogledu samo ikona, ako ne znate šta određena ikona znači, možete držati "
"miš preko ikone, i nakon sekundu ili tako, mala naznaka će iskočiti u "
"označenom teksutalnom okviru."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Orientation</guilabel> item in the popup menu has to do with "
"the placement of the toolbar. You can choose any of the four sides of the "
"&stage; window."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Orijentacijska</guilabel> stavka u iskočnom izborniku ima veze sa "
"postavljanjem alatne trake. Možete odabrati bilo koji od četiri strane "
"&stage; prozora."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &stage; menus are discussed in the following sections."
msgstr "&stage; meni su spomenuti u sljedećim poglavljima."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Menu"
msgstr "Meni datoteke"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Begins a new presentation.</action> The startup dialog will open, "
"allowing you to choose a template for your presentation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Počni novu prezentaciju.</action> Početni dijalog će se otvoriti, "
"dozvoljavajući vam da izaberete šablon za vašu prezentaciju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Otvori...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens an existing presentation.</action> A standard &kde; file open "
"dialog will appear, allowing you to choose a file to open."
msgstr ""
"<action>Otvara postojeću prezentaciju.</action> Standardni &kde; dijalog "
"otvaranja datoteke će se pojaviti, omogućavajući vam da izaberete datoteku "
"koju želite otvoriti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Open Recent</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Otvori nedavno</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a list of recently opened files for you to choose from."
msgstr "Prikazuje listu nedavno korištenih datoteka za vas da možete odabrati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap> </keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap> </keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spasi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Saves the currently open presentation.</action> If you have not "
"previously saved it, you will be asked to name the file. If you have "
"previously saved the presentation, it will be resaved with the same name."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spasi trenutno otvorenu prezentaciju.</action> Ako je niste "
"prethodni spasili, bit ćete upitani da date ime datoteci. Ako ste prethodno "
"spasili prezentaciju, bit će sačuvana pod istim imenom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Snimi kao...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the currently open presentation with a new name."
msgstr "Spašava trenutno otvorenu prezentaciju sa novim imenom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Dokument</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Osvježi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload the currently active file."
msgstr "Ponovo učitaj trenutno aktivnu datoteku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Učitaj...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import a presentation that was previously created in one of several common "
"formats."
msgstr ""
"Učitaj prezentaciju koja je prethodno kreirana u jednom od nekoliko "
"uobičajenih formata."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvoz...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Export the currently open presentation to one of several common formats for "
"use in another application, or for exchange with someone who does not have "
"access to &stage;."
msgstr ""
"Izvozi trenutno otvorenu prezentaciju na jedan od nekoliko uobičajenih "
"formata za upotrebu u drugoj aplikaciji, ili za razmjenu sa nekim ko nema "
"pristup &stage;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mail...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mail...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open</action> a new email message in your selected email client with "
"the current &stage; document attached."
msgstr ""
"<action>Otvori</action> novu email poruku u vašem odabranom email klijentu "
"sa trenutnim &stage; dokumentom u prilogu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export as HTML...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvedi kao HTML...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Starts the HTML wizard</action>, which is described in the section "
"<xref linkend=\"html-wizard\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pokreni HTML čarobnjaka</action>, koji je opisan u dijelu <xref "
"linkend=\"html-wizard\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Prints the presentation</action>. More precisely, it opens the print "
"settings dialog, where you can adjust the settings before printing your "
"presentation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Printaj prezentaciju</action>. Preciznije, otvara dijalog print "
"postavki, gdje možete podesiti postavke prije printanja vaše prezentacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print Preview...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pregled prije štampanja...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays the presentation</action> with a viewer, exactly as it "
"would look if printed."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži prezentaciju</action> sa preglednikom, tačno kako bi "
"izgledalo ako se odštampa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Document Information</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Informacije o dokumentu</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows you to enter information about the document.</action> This "
"includes information about the author, and an abstract on the documents "
"contents."
msgstr ""
"<action>Dopušta da unesete informacije o dokumentu.</action> Ovo uključuje "
"informacije o autoru, i sažetan sadržaja dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zatvori</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Close the current presentation.</action> You will be given an "
"opportunity to save any changes first."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zatvori trenutnu prezentaciju.</action> Bit će vam pružena prilika "
"da prvo spasite bilo koje promjene."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izlaz</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Close</action> &stage;. You will be given an opportunity to save all "
"changes in all open presentations first."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zatvori</action> &stage;. Bit će vam pružena prilika da prvo spasite "
"sve promjene u svim otvorenim prezentacijama."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Izmijeni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo: <replaceable>Last task</"
"replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poništi: "
"<replaceable>Zadnji zadatak</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last action you performed."
msgstr "Poništi zadnju obavljenu akciju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo: "
"<replaceable>Last undone task</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vrati: "
"<replaceable>Zadnji poništen zadatak</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Redo the last action you undid.</action> If you have not undone any "
"actions, or the last undo action is not reversible, this menu item is "
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"<action>Vrati zadnju akciju koju ste poništili.</action> Ako niste poništili "
"nijednu akciju, ili je zadnju radnju nije moguće poništiti, ova stavka meni "
"je onemogućena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Isijeci</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the selected item to the clipboard, and remove it from the document."
msgstr "Kopiraj selektovanu stavku u međuspremnik, i obriši je iz dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the selected item to the clipboard, while leaving it intact in your "
"presentation."
msgstr ""
"Kopiraj selektovanu stavku u međuspremnik, ostavljajući je netaknutu u "
"prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Umetni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert the contents of the clipboard into your presentation."
msgstr "Umetni sadržaj međuspremnika u vašu prezentaciju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the currently selected item from your presentation."
msgstr "Obriši trenutno selektovanu stavku iz vaše prezentacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odaberi Sve</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select all the objects and text on the current slide."
msgstr "Selektuj sve objekte i tekst na trenutnom slajdu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselect</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselekt</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deselect any currently selected objects."
msgstr "Deselektuj bilo koji trenutno selektovani objekat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pronađi...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search for text within the presentation."
msgstr "Traži tekst u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F3</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F3</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nađi sljedeći</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find the next occurrence of a piece of text within a presentation."
msgstr "Nađi sljedeće pojavljivanje dijela teksta u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nađi prethodni</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find the previous occurrence of a piece of text within a presentation."
msgstr "Nađi prethodno pojavljivanje dijela teksta u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Replace...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zamijeni...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replace one or more occurrences of a piece of text in your presentation with "
"a different piece of text."
msgstr ""
"Zamijeni jedno ili više pojavljivanja dijela teksta u vašoj prezentaciji sa "
"drugim dijelom teksta."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Prikaz Meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pregled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novi pregled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens another window with the same presentation loaded</action> so "
"you can work on more than one slide at a time."
msgstr ""
"<action>Otvara drugi prozor sa učitanom istom operacijom</action> tako da "
"možete raditi na više od jednog slajda."

#. Tag: term
#: menus.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F5</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Normal</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Notes</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Slides Sorter</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F5</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Normal</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Bilješke</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razvrstač slajdova</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch with these actions between the view modes Normal, where you edit "
"slides, Notes, which shows a slide preview with a textbox for your "
"annotations for the actual slide and the Slides Sorter view, where you can "
"rename, cut, copy and paste slides and arrange them for your presentation."
msgstr ""
"Mijenjajte sa ovim akcijama između normalnog načina pregleda, gdje možete "
"izmijeniti slajdove, Bilješke, koje omogućavaju prikaz slajdova sa okvirom "
"za tekst za napomene za određeni slajd i Razvrstač slajdova pogled, gdje "
"možete preimenovati, isijeci, kopirati i umetnuti slajdove i organizovati ih "
"za vašu prezentaciju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F8</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Master Slides</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F8</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži master slajdove</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle the display of the slide master</action> where you can put "
"objects that you want to appear on each slide in your presentation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prebaci ekran sa master slajda</action> gdje možete staviti objekte "
"koje želite da se pojave na svakom slajdu u vašoj prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Grid</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži rešetku</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &stage; will display a grid of dots representing the "
"intersections of imaginary horizontal and vertical lines. You can use these "
"dots to precisely position objects on the slide."
msgstr ""
"Ako omogućen &stage; će pokazati rešetku tački koje predstavljaju presjeke "
"imaginarnih horizontalnih i vertikalnih linija. Možete koristiti ove tačke "
"za precizno pozicioniranje objekata na slajdu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem> Snap to Grid</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem> Šćepaj umrežu</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is enabled, when dropping or moving objects on the slide the top "
"left corner of the object will <quote>snap</quote> or move, to the nearest "
"grid point."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ovo omogućeno, prilikom puštanja i micanja objekata na slajdu gornji "
"lijevi čošak objekta će <quote>šćepati</quote> ili se pomaći, ka najbližoj "
"tački na mreži."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This does reduce your freedom to freely position objects on the slide, "
"however it also helps to line up objects precisely. It is easily disabled or "
"enabled with this menu entry, allowing you the best of both worlds."
msgstr ""
"Ovo smanjuje vašu slobodnu da slobodno pozicionirate objekte na slajdu, no "
"također pomaže da se postroje objekti precizno. Lako se deaktivira ili "
"aktivirana sa ovim meni unosom, omogućavajući vam najbolje od oba svijeta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Guides</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži vodiče</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When working in &stage; you can drag a <quote>guide line</quote> from either "
"the horizontal or vertical ruler onto your document. This guide-line will "
"not print or display in the finished presentation, it is simply to help you "
"align objects on screen. If this item is enabled, these guide lines will be "
"visible. If this is disabled, they will not be visible."
msgstr ""
"Kada radite u &stage; možete povući <quote>vodič crtu</quote> iz bilo "
"horizontalnog ili vertikalnog linijara na vaš dokument. Ova vodić-linija se "
"neće štampati niti prikazati u gotovoj prezentaciji, ona je jednostavno tu "
"da vam pomogne poravnati objekte na ekranu. Ako je ova stavka omogućena, ove "
"vodič linije će biti vidljive. Ako nije omogućena, neće biti vidljive."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Guide lines work across slides, allowing you to align objects the same way "
"across multiple slides."
msgstr ""
"Vodič linije rade preko slajdova, dopuštajući vam da poravnate objekte na "
"isti način na više slajdova."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disabling (hiding) guide lines does not delete them. If you have created "
"guide lines, and then disabled this item, enabling it again will retain the "
"guide lines you created."
msgstr ""
"Deaktiviranje (sakrivanje) vodič linije ih ne briše. Ako ste kreirali vodič "
"linije, onda deaktivirali ove stavke, ponovno aktiviranje će zadržati vodič "
"linije koje ste kreirali."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pregled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zumiranje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu allows you to zoom in or out of the slide. Several predefined "
"zoom levels are available, including <guimenuitem>Fit Page</guimenuitem> to "
"scale the entire slide so as to be visible in the size window you have open, "
"and <guimenuitem>Fit Page Width</guimenuitem> to scale the slide so it fills "
"the entire width of the window, although you may now have to scroll "
"vertically. There are also several other scaling choices, from "
"<guimenuitem>33%</guimenuitem> up to <guimenuitem>500%</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj podmeni dozvoljava da zumirate unutra ili izvan slajda. Nekoliko "
"predefinisanih nivoa zumiranja su dostupni, uključujući "
"<guimenuitem>Pristaje stranici</guimenuitem> da izmjeri čitav slajd tako da "
"bude vidljiv u veličini prozora koji ste otvorili, i <guimenuitem>Pristaje "
"širini stranice</guimenuitem> da izmjeri slajd tako da popuni čitavu širinu "
"prozira, iako ćete sada možda morati skrolati vertikalno. Postoje još neki "
"izbori mjerenja od <guimenuitem>33%</guimenuitem> do <guimenuitem>500%</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Menu"
msgstr "Unesi Meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Insert</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Variable</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Unesi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Varijabla</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can insert a variable that is filled in with a value that may be "
"updated as you update the document."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete unijeti varijablu koja je popunjena sa vrijednošću koja može "
"biti izmjenjena dok ažurirate dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import Slideshow...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Unesi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvezi prezentaciju...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Insert an already existing presentation.</action> A standard &kde; "
"file open dialog will appear, allowing you to choose a "
"<guilabel>OpenDocument Presentation</guilabel> (.odp), which will be "
"inserted after the last slide in your current presentation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ubaci već potojeću prezentaciju.</action> Standardni &kde; dijalog "
"za otvaranje datoteke će se pojaviti, omogućavajući vam da izaberete "
"<guilabel>OpenDocument Prezentacija</guilabel> (.odp), koji će biti ubačen "
"nakon zadnjeg slajda u trenutnoj prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Insert</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Insert Pictures as Slides...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Unesi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ubaci slike kao slajdove...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this menu item to insert one or more pictures, each is inserted on a new "
"slide. This is useful for the people who want to use &stage; to make a slide "
"show."
msgstr ""
"Koristite ovu stavku menija za ubacivanje jedne ili više slika, svaki je "
"ubačen u novi slajd. Ovo je korisno za ljude koji žele koristiti &stage; da "
"naprave prezentaciju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Insert</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Scan Image...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Unesi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skeniraj sliku...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Scan an image with a scanner.</action> This requires you have a "
"scanner installed. It opens a scan dialog to allow the use of the scanner."
msgstr ""
"<action>Skeniraj sliku skenerom.</action> Ovo zahtjeva da imate skener "
"instaliran. Otvara dijalog za skeniranje da omogući korištenje ovog skenera."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format Menu"
msgstr "Format Meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Font...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Font...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Select Font</guilabel> dialog contains options for selected "
"segments of text."
msgstr ""
"The <guilabel>Odaberite Font</guilabel> dijalog sadrži opcije za selektovane "
"segmente teksta."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this dialog, you can <action>change the font, style and size of "
"selected text</action>. The <interface>preview box</interface> at the bottom "
"allows you to <action>approximate changes before you make them</action>."
msgstr ""
"Sa ovim dijalogom, možete <action>promijeniti font, stil i veličinu "
"selektovanog teksta</action>. <interface>Okvir za prikaz</interface> na dnu "
"omogućuje vam da <action>vidite promjene prije nego ih napravite</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paragraph...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paragraf...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Paragraph Format</guilabel> dialog contains settings for "
"larger blocks of text, such as paragraphs. Using this dialog, you can set "
"indenting, line spacing, bullet/numbered list and border settings."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Paragraf Format</guilabel> dijalog sadrži postavke za veće blokove "
"teksta, kao što su paragrafi. Koristeći ovaj dijalog, možete postaviti "
"uvlačenje, razmak, neoznačena/numerisana lista i ivične postavke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Style Manager</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravitelj "
"stila</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Style Manager</guilabel> allows you to create an entire set of "
"attributes that will be applied to selected text all at once."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Upravitelj stila</guilabel> omogućava da kreirate čitav set "
"atributa koji će biti primjenjeni na selektovani tekst odjednom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1325
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Page Layout...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izgled stranice...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to set the page details. You can specify the margins, the "
"orientation, either portrait (higher than wide) or Landscape (wider than "
"high) formats. There are many templates, such as screen, A4, US legal."
msgstr ""
"Omogućava da postavite detalje stranice. Možete specificirati margine, "
"orijentaciju, ili protret(više nego šire) ili pejzaž (šire nego više) "
"formate. Postoji mnogo šablona, kao za ekran, A4, US legal."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slide Menu"
msgstr "Slajd meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Slide</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Insert Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ubaci slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a new slide after the current one."
msgstr "Ubaci novi slajd nakon trenutnog."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1676
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Slide</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy the current slide to the clipboard."
msgstr "Kopiraj trenutni slajd u međurezultat."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1688
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Slide</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Obriši slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Delete the current page from the presentation.</action> You will be "
"asked to confirm this action."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obriši trenutnu stranicu iz prezentacije.</action> Bit ćete upitani "
"da potvrdite ovu akciju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PageUp</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Slide</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Previous Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PageUp</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prethodni slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1707
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go back to the previous slide in the slide show."
msgstr "Idi nazad na prethodni slajd u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PageDown</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Slide</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Next Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PageDown</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Sljedeći slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next slide in the slide show."
msgstr "Idi na sljedeći slajd u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slide</guimenu> <guimenuitem>First Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prvi slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go directly to the first slide in the slide show."
msgstr "Idi direktno na prvi slajd u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>End</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slide</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Last Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>End</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zadnji slajd</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1746
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go immediately to the final slide in the slide show."
msgstr "Idi odmah na zadnji slajd u prezentaciji."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1753
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slide Show Menu"
msgstr "Prikaz slajda meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slide Show</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Start Presentation</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>From Current Slide</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Prikaz slajda</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Počni prezentaciju</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Od trenutnog slajda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Begin the slideshow from the current slide."
msgstr "Počni prezentaciju od trenutnog slajda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Slide Show</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Start Presentation</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>From First Slide</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Prikaz slajda</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Počni prezentaciju</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Od prvog slajda</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1781
#, no-c-format
msgid "Begin the slideshow from the first slide."
msgstr "Počni prezentaciju od prvog slajda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Slide Show</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Slide Show...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Prikaz slajda</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriši prikaz slajda...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set up the properties for the entire slide show here, including "
"whether to show the duration on screen, which of the slides in a "
"presentation to include, and several other global settings."
msgstr ""
"Možete podesiti postavke za čitavu prezentaciju slajdova ovdje, uključujući "
"da li da pokažete trajanje na ekranu, koji od slajdova u prezentaciji da "
"uključite, i nekoliko drugih globalnih postavki."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1851
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni Postavki"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1853
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu allows you to customize &stage;."
msgstr ""
"The <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> meni omogućuje da kostumizirate &stage;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1860
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show Toolbar</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži alatnu traku</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1866
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this menu you can both enable and disable the display of toolbar."
msgstr ""
"U ovom meniju možete oboje aktivirati ili deaktivirati prikaz alatne trake."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriši prečice...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts</guimenuitem> allows you to assign a "
"keyboard shortcut to actions that &stage; menus or icons contain."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriši prečice</guimenuitem> vam omogućava da dodjelite "
"prečicu na tastaturi za akcije koje &stage; meni ili ikone sadrže."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customize Shortcuts"
msgstr "Podesite prečice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1895
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing the shortcuts"
msgstr "Prilagođavanje prečica"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to assign a shortcut that is already used, it will give you a "
"warning message. Highlight what you want to do (in the picture, I have "
"chosen to make a keyboard shortcut to <guilabel>About KDE</guilabel>)."
msgstr ""
"Ako pokušate dodijeliti prečicu koja se već koristi, pojavit će se poruka "
"upozorenja. Označite šta želite uraditi (na slici, ja sam izabrao da "
"napravim prečicu za tastaturu za <guilabel>O KDE</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the radio button to the <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> key setting and "
"type the key you want to use. I assigned <keycap>Control</keycap> key and "
"<keycap>Y</keycap> to bring up the <quote>About KDE</quote> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite taster na <guilabel>Vlastite</guilabel> postavke tastera i unesite "
"taster koji želite koristiti. Ja sam dodijelio  <keycap>Control</keycap> "
"taster i  <keycap>Y</keycap> za dovođenje <quote>O KDE</quote> dijalog "
"okvira."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The button shows what has been assigned. Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to "
"make the changes, click <guibutton>Default</guibutton> to restore whatever "
"was assigned as default, click <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to do nothing "
"and leave the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dugme pokazuje ono što je dodijeljeno. Kliknite <guibutton>OK</guibutton> da "
"napravite promjene, kliknite  <guibutton>Zadano</guibutton> za vraćanje onog "
"što je postavljeno kao zadano, kliknite <guibutton>Otkaži</guibutton> da ne "
"radi ništa i napusti dijalog."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriši alatne trake...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure Toolbars allows you to add or delete icons on each of the toolbars."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguriši alatne trake omogućava vam da dodata ili obrišete ikone na "
"svakoj alatnoj traci."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1931
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configuring &stage; toolbars</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfigurisanje &stage; alatnih traka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1937
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configuring &stage; toolbars</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurisanje &stage; alatnih traka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top is a drop down box to enable you to choose which toolbar you want "
"to modify. In the picture the <guilabel>File</guilabel> toolbar is selected. "
"If I want to add the <guiicon>Dockers</guiicon> icon to that toolbar, I "
"click the entry in the left window. The arrow pointing right becomes "
"available, if I click the arrow the <guiicon>Dockers</guiicon> entry is "
"added to the selected toolbar. The left arrow is available when you click in "
"the right side window. It allows you to remove an icon from a toolbar. The "
"up and down arrows become active when an item on the right side is selected. "
"You can also move the highlight in the right side window up and down with "
"the keyboard arrow keys. By clicking on the arrows with the mouse you can "
"change the order of the entries in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu je padajući okvir za omogućavanje odabira koju alatnu traku želite "
"modifikovati. Na slici <guilabel>Datoteka</guilabel> alatna traka je "
"selektovana. Ako želim dodati  <guiicon>Dokovi</guiicon> ikonu na tu alatnu "
"traku, kliknut ću ulaz u lijevom prozoru. Strelica koja pokazuje desno "
"postaje dostupna, ako kliknem strelicu <guiicon>Dokovi</guiicon> ulaz je "
"dodan na selektovanu alatnu traku. Lijeva strelica je dostupna kada kliknete "
"na desnu stranu prozora. Omogućava vam da obrišete ikonu sa alatne trake. "
"Strelice gore i dole postaju aktivne kada je stavka na desnoj strani "
"selektovana. Možete također pomicati istaknuto na desnoj strani prozora gore "
"i dole sa strelicama na tastaturi. Klikom na strelice sa mišem možete "
"promijeniti redoslijed unosa u meniju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1961
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Themes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teme</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Choose the color theme for &stage; window.</action> You can choose "
"one of the predefined color schemes or select <guimenuitem>Configuration...</"
"guimenuitem> to open <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors\">&systemsettings; "
"color selection module</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Promijeni boju teme &stage; prozora.</action> Možete odabrati jednu "
"od predefinisanih shema boja ili označiti <guimenuitem>Konfiguracija...</"
"guimenuitem> za otvaranje <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors"
"\">&systemsettings; modul izbora boja</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Stage...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kofiguriši stage...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the <link linkend=\"configure-dialog\">Configure &stage;</link> section "
"for a complete explanation of all &stage; settings."
msgstr ""
"Vidi <link linkend=\"configure-dialog\">Konfiguriši &stage;</link> poglavlje "
"za potpuno objašnjenje za sve &stage; postavke."

